Plot: The story revolves around the death of Poornima Rao, a senior executive in a reputed IT firm, who dies jumping of the high raised IT tech park while taking a selfie.
Title: Selfie
Writer: Phani Kotaprolu (story), Phani Kotaprolu (screenplay), Phani Kotaprolu (dialogue), Arjun Ramu (lyricist)
Actors: Trilokk Shroff, Deepa Gowda, Pooja Kamath, Namratha Gauraklar
